<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 12:23:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商受到欧盟关税打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-based-ev-makers-hit-with-european-union-tariffs-2024-06-12/</link><description>欧盟委员会周三通知汽车制造商，将从下个月起对进口的中国电动汽车征收高达 38.1% 的额外关税，此举可能会招致中国的报复。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 11:26:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-based-ev-makers-hit-with-european-union-tariffs-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国蔚来汽车表示，尽管关税增加，但对欧洲电动汽车市场的承诺“坚定不移”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-says-commitment-europe-ev-market-unwavering-despite-increased-tariffs-2024-06-12/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车周三表示，强烈反对欧盟利用提高关税作为阻碍正常全球电动汽车贸易的策略，但其对欧洲电动汽车市场的承诺坚定不移。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 11:05:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-nio-says-commitment-europe-ev-market-unwavering-despite-increased-tariffs-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>足球检察官要求撤销对AC米兰中国前老板的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/soccer-prosecutors-ask-drop-case-against-ac-milans-chinese-former-owner-2024-06-12/</link><description>据知情人士透露，米兰检察官已要求对前AC米兰老板李勇鸿提起虚假会计指控，经过长时间调查后，该案应撤销。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 10:41:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/soccer-prosecutors-ask-drop-case-against-ac-milans-chinese-former-owner-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>李总理访澳新西兰对中国更加警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-nz-more-wary-china-premier-li-visits-2024-06-12/</link><description>当中国总理李强本周访问新西兰和澳大利亚时，地区安全担忧将掩盖利润丰厚的贸易关系，其气氛与七年前中国总理上次访问时的气氛明显不同。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 10:22:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-nz-more-wary-china-premier-li-visits-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对中国加征关税：全球反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/view-eu-impose-duties-up-38-chinese-electric-vehicles-2024-06-12/</link><description>欧盟委员会周三表示，将对进口中国电动汽车征收高达38.1%的临时关税，此举可能会招致中国的报复。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 10:10:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/view-eu-impose-duties-up-38-chinese-electric-vehicles-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：这次反弹能对抗美联储吗？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-12/</link><description>市场通讯员 Naomi Rovnick 展望美国和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 10:04:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对中国电动汽车征收最高38%的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-sets-duties-chinese-electric-vehicles-up-38-2024-06-12/</link><description>欧盟委员会周三宣布将对中国电动汽车进口征收高达38.1%的临时关税，此举可能会招致中国的严厉批评并可能遭到报复。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 09:57:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-sets-duties-chinese-electric-vehicles-up-38-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>北京降低关税后，澳大利亚对中国的葡萄酒出口猛增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australian-wine-exports-china-rocket-after-beijing-drops-tariffs-2024-06-12/</link><description>贸易部长周三表示，在北京取消关税后的一个月内，澳大利亚葡萄酒制造商向中国出口了价值 8600 万澳元（合 5700 万美元）的葡萄酒，应该对未来的销售量充满信心。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 09:09:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/australian-wine-exports-china-rocket-after-beijing-drops-tariffs-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>拜登前往七国集团峰会重点讨论乌克兰援助、中国对俄罗斯的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-heads-g7-summit-focused-ukraine-aid-chinas-support-russia-2024-06-12/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周三飞往意大利与七国集团领导人举行会议，旨在就俄罗斯对乌克兰的战争和中国对莫斯科的支持和过剩的工业产能加大对俄罗斯的压力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 09:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-heads-g7-summit-focused-ukraine-aid-chinas-support-russia-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对电动汽车征收关税迫在眉睫，中国准备捍卫利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ready-defend-interests-eu-tariffs-evs-loom-2024-06-12/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，在有报纸报道欧盟委员会将对进口中国电动汽车征收高达25%的关税后，中国将采取一切必要措施“坚定维护”自己的合法权益。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 09:07:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ready-defend-interests-eu-tariffs-evs-loom-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡顶级银行星展银行高管称，到 2026 年财富资产目标将达到 3700 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-top-bank-dbs-eyes-370-bln-wealth-assets-by-2026-top-exec-says-2024-06-12/</link><description>星展集团负责人表示，星展集团计划到 2026 年底将其财富业务管理的资产增加至 5000 亿新元（合 3697 亿美元），因为这家新加坡顶级银行押注资金将强劲流入新加坡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 08:50:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-top-bank-dbs-eyes-370-bln-wealth-assets-by-2026-top-exec-says-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税后，欧洲汽车股受到报复担忧的打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-car-manufacturers-fall-following-uk-dieselgate-lawsuits-2024-06-12/</link><description>在欧盟委员会表示将对进口中国电动汽车征收关税后，由于担心中国的报复，欧洲一些最大汽车制造商的股价周三下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 07:59:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-car-manufacturers-fall-following-uk-dieselgate-lawsuits-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>印度4-5月钢铁进口量创五年新高 内需旺盛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-april-may-steel-imports-hit-five-year-high-buoyant-domestic-demand-2024-06-12/</link><description>路透社看到的临时政府数据显示，在四月份开始的财政年度的前两个月，印度成品钢材进口量触及五年来新高，该国仍然是净进口国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 07:10:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-april-may-steel-imports-hit-five-year-high-buoyant-domestic-demand-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将对中国电动汽车加征高达38%的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-impose-multi-billion-euro-tariffs-chinese-evs-ft-reports-2024-06-12/</link><description>欧盟委员会周三告诉汽车制造商，将从 7 月起对进口中国电动汽车征收高达 38.1% 的额外关税，此举被中国称为保护主义，但中国汽车行业认为不会产生重大影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 04:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-impose-multi-billion-euro-tariffs-chinese-evs-ft-reports-2024-06-12/</guid></item><item><title>世界银行称缅甸贫困加剧，经济增长停滞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/myanmar-poverty-deepens-economic-growth-stagnant-world-bank-says-2024-06-12/</link><description>世界银行周三表示，缅甸的贫困现象比过去六年中任何时候都更加普遍，这个饱受冲突蹂躏的国家本财年的经济增长可能仍保持在区区 1%，而且几乎看不到任何喘息的迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 04:38:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/myanmar-poverty-deepens-economic-growth-stagnant-world-bank-says-2024-06-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>